import {
  Box,
  TextField,
  MenuItem,
  FormControl,
  Typography,
  Grid,
  // Divider,
  Chip,
} from "@mui/material";
import Divider from "@mui/material/Divider";
import { LoadingButton } from "@mui/lab";

const Register = () => {
  return (
    <Box
      component="div"
      sx={{
        display: "flex",
        flexDirection: "column",
        flexWrap: "wrap",
        maxWidth: 600,
        border: ".1px solid black",
        borderRadius: ".3rem",
      }}
      mt={12}
      ml="auto"
      mr="auto"
      p={5}
      gap={2}
    >
      <Typography variant="h3" fontWeight="bold">
        Creare cont
      </Typography>
      <Box component="form">
        <Grid container spacing={2}>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl sx={{ width: "100%" }}>
              <TextField
                type="text"
                label="Nume"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl sx={{ width: "100%" }}>
              <TextField
                type="email"
                label="Email"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl sx={{ width: "100%" }}>
              <TextField
                type="password"
                label="Parolă"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={6}>
            <FormControl sx={{ width: "100%" }}>
              <TextField
                type="password"
                label="Confirmare parolă"
                variant="outlined"
                size="small"
              />
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={12}>
            <FormControl>
              <TextField
                label="Sex"
                variant="outlined"
                select
                sx={{ width: 75 }}
                value=""
                size="small"
              >
                <MenuItem value=""></MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value="m">M</MenuItem>
                <MenuItem value="f">F</MenuItem>
              </TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Divider light style={{ width: "100%" }} textAlign="center">
            <Chip label="Detalii fizic" size="small" />
          </Divider>
          <Grid item xs={4}>
            <FormControl>
              <TextField></TextField>
            </FormControl>
          </Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4}></Grid>
          <Grid item xs={4}></Grid>
        </Grid>
      </Box>
      <LoadingButton
        variant="contained"
        loadingPosition="center"
        sx={{
          fontSize: "1rem",
          alignSelf: "flex-start",
          textTransform: "capitalize",
          backgroundColor: "secondary.main",
          "&:hover": { backgroundColor: "secondary.main" },
        }}
      >
        Înregistrare
      </LoadingButton>
    </Box>
  );
};

export default Register;
